<section class="faq section" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What areas do you service?</summary>
        <p>Queensland, primarily Brisbane, Gold Coast, and Bali</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Who do you service?</summary>
        <p>Time-poor professionals, first home buyers ($550,000), to luxury home buyers (up to $7,000,000)</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Why should I engage a Buyers Agent?</summary>
        <p>Represents client interests, provides market insights, access to pre-market properties, no monetary incentives from third parties</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .faq h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-subtle);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--body-large);
    color: var(--primary-green);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 24px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    content: 'âˆ’';
  }

  .faq-item p {
    margin-top: 15px;
    padding-top: 15px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
</style>
